HEADWORD: Peptonuria
<hw>Pep`to*nu"ri*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. See
<er>Peptone</er>, and <er>Urine</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>The
